###2026.06.11.09
- Release: Promote the full `2026.05.27.01` through `2026.06.11.08` development cycle to the stable `main` channel while keeping the manifest, CA feed, package archive, and plugin install link pointed at `main`
- UX: Rework the cleanup dashboard around clearer `Ready`, `Needs review`, `Blocked`, and `Ignored` outcomes, merge search/sort/filter controls, remove the scanned appdata paths block, simplify row badges/actions, and keep the Controls panel focused on Rescan, Cleanup Options, and Help
