- Support: Add per-phase scan timing metrics for settings load, Docker state/query, template scan, filesystem discovery, filtering, row build, and snapshot write
- Support: Tighten diagnostics log matching so unrelated `emhttpd` startup/pool noise is excluded while plugin, PHP-FPM, nginx, timeout, and error context stays included
